dict.string: Automatically sync with iTunes on your computer when your iPad is plugged in to power and connected to Wi‑Fi.
Automatically sync with iTunes on your computer when your iPhone is plugged in to power and connected to Wi‑Fi.

To enable Wi-Fi syncing with iTunes, connect to iTunes on your computer using a cable and click “Sync with this iPad over Wi‑Fi”.

To enable Wi-Fi syncing with iTunes, connect to iTunes on your computer using a cable and click “Sync with this iPod over Wi‑Fi”.
To enable WLAN syncing with iTunes, connect to iTunes on your computer using a cable and click “Sync with this iPad over WLAN”.

To enable WLAN syncing with iTunes, connect to iTunes on your computer using a cable and click “Sync with this iPod over WLAN”.
Sync will resume when “%@” is available.
